extends ../ui_layout

block content

  .ui.text.container.addBottomMargin
    br      
    .ui.raised.segment
      h3.ui.header
        i.book.blue.icon
        .content
          | Learn
      hr
      .ui.basic.segment.removePadding
        .ui.mini.green.right.labeled.icon.button.showLearnSectionButton
          i.down.arrow.icon
          |   Next
      .ui.basic.segment.learnSegment.hidden
        h5.ui.header
          i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
          .content
            | <b>Online Shopping</b> has become popular due to its convenience and simplicity
        h5.ui.header
          i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
          .content
            | As more people turn to digital shopping, there are concerns about their safety as this medium is susceptible to threats 
        h5.ui.header
          i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
          .content
            | Online shoping security threats include Unecrypted Data, Adware, Identity Theft, and Data Breaches 
        .ui.mini.green.right.labeled.icon.button.showKeyTermsButton
          i.down.arrow.icon
          |   Next
    
    .ui.segment.keyIdeasSegment.hidden
      h3.ui.header
        i.key.blue.icon
        .content Key Ideas
      .sub.header 
        i.hand.pointer.icon.grayElement
        span.grayElement Click on each word below to learn more
      br
      .ui.stackable.two.column.grid
        .ui.column
          .keyTerm.ui.raised.segment.voiceover_keyTerm1
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Unecrypted Data
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition  
              | unprotected information that is easily readable
              ul 
                | When you input sensitive data like your credit card details on a website, you expect that your data is secured with proper encryption within the web application. But that's not always the case. 
        .ui.column
          .keyTerm.ui.raised.segment.voiceover_keyTerm2
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Adware
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition 
              | software that automatically displays or downloads unwanted advertising material
              ul 
                | Cybercriminals can use adware it to launch attacks. Adware could be encrypted with malware to lure you to malicious websites. When you arrive on the website, they'll request your personal information—including your credit card details. 
        .ui.column
          .keyTerm.ui.raised.segment.voiceover_keyTerm3
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Identity Theft
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition 
              | When someone uses another person's personal identifying information, like their name, identifying number, or credit card number
              ul 
                | One of the most common security risks of online shopping is identity theft. Cybercriminals can hack into private websites and steal users’ login credentials or credit card details. If they aren't impersonating users by making unauthorized purchases, they’re selling off their personal information online.  
        .ui.column
          .keyTerm.ui.raised.segment.voiceover_keyTerm3
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Data Breaches 
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition 
              | A security violation, in which sensitive, protected or confidential data is copied, transmitted, viewed, stolen or used by an individual unauthorized to do so
              ul 
                | A data breach occurs when hackers gain unauthorized access to data in web applications. When you enter your personal information into websites as you shop online, you stand a risk of having your information exposed in the event of a data breach.  
    
    
    .ui.warning.message#clickNextWarning
      .header
       | Click "Next"
    .ui.warning.message#clickLabelsWarning
     .header
      | Click on each label to proceed   
    a(href='javascript:void(0);', onclick='javascript:clickGotIt();')
        .ui.labeled.icon.button
            i.rocket.icon
            |   Got it!

